# Auto detect text files and perform LF normalization
* text=auto

- **index.html**: The main HTML file that contains the structure of the game.
- **style.css**: The CSS file that styles the game.
- **scripts.js**: The JavaScript file that contains the game logic.
- **feature.js**: Additional JavaScript file for handling UI features.
- **.gitattributes**: Configuration file for Git.

## How to Play

1. Open `index.html` in your web browser.
2. Enter your name(s) and select the game mode (Single or Duo).
3. Click the "Start" button to begin the game.
4. Take turns clicking on the grid to place your mark (X or O).
5. The game will announce the winner or if it's a draw.

## Features

- Single and Duo player modes.
- Responsive design for different screen sizes.
- Celebration message for the winner.

## Getting Started

To get started with this project, you can clone the repository and open the `index.html` file in your web browser.

```sh
git clone https://github.com/your-username/tic-tac-toe-game.git
cd tic-tac-toe-game